"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Move level up</emph>. With the cursor positioned in front of a paragraph with paragraph style вҖңHeading XвҖқ (X = 2вҖ“10), the outline level is moved up one level. For list paragraphs, the list level is moved up one level."
